cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to a string value instead of an integer will cause a configuration parsing error during CU initialization.

du.explanation_en: Setting Asn1_verbosity to an unknown enumeration value will cause configuration validation failure in the DU component.
du.explanation_zh: 將 Asn1_verbosity 設定為未知的枚舉值將導致 DU 元件中的配置驗證失敗。
